<%- include('partials/head', { title: 'Cancellation & Refund Policy - EduLearn' }) %>
<%- include('partials/navbar') %>
<main class="container py-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-10">
            <h1 class="mb-4">No Refund Policy</h1>
            
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <h5 class="card-title text-primary mb-3">All Sales Are Final</h5>
                    <p>We want to be completely transparent with our customers. Please note that all course purchases on EduLearn are final and non-refundable. By making a purchase, you acknowledge and agree to this no-refund policy.</p>
                    
                    <div class="alert alert-warning">
                        <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle me-2"></i>
                        <strong>Important:</strong> Due to the digital nature of our products, we do not offer refunds or exchanges for any purchased courses or subscriptions.
                    </div>
                    
                    <h6 class="mt-4 mb-3">Before You Purchase:</h6>
                    <p>We encourage you to:</p>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-primary me-2"></i> Review the course description and curriculum carefully</li>
                        <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-primary me-2"></i> Check the course preview if available</li>
                        <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-primary me-2"></i> Ensure your device meets the technical requirements</li>
                        <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-primary me-2"></i> Contact us if you have any questions before purchasing</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <div class="mt-4">
                        <p class="mb-2"><strong>Note:</strong> EduLearn currently does not offer subscription plans. All courses are available for one-time purchase only.</p>
                        <p class="mb-0">For any questions or concerns, please contact our <a href="/contact" class="text-primary">support team</a>.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
<%- include('partials/scripts') %>
